',0,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=39',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(41,1,'2022-10-24 10:49:48','2022-10-23 23:49:48','https://youtu.be/PdhukMjIEo4','SIT283 - Assessment 2 - Marine Park - Showcase Video','','publish','open','open','','sit283-assessment-2-marine-park-showcase-video','','','2023-04-24 10:50:24','2023-04-24 00:50:24','',0,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=41',0,'post','',0),(42,1,'2023-04-24 10:49:48','2023-04-24 00:49:48','https://youtu.be/PdhukMjIEo4','SIT283 - Assessment 2 - Marine Park - Showcase Video','','inherit','closed','closed','','41-revision-v1','','','2023-04-24 10:49:48','2023-04-24 00:49:48','',41,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=42',0,'revision','',0),(43,1,'2023-04-24 10:56:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<h1>Introduction</h1>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Concept: Marine Park</li>\r\n 	<li>Context of the Concept:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe idea of constructing this underwater world came from an animation I watched when I was a child, called Future Boy Conan, which tells the story of the protagonist and his grandfather living on an island after more than half of the earth\'s land was destroyed in a war. In the early stages of the story, the underwater ruins are impressive, this scenario may be as anti-war propaganda, perhaps can make people recall childhood memories, or can be as simple as an experience of visiting ruins in the underwater world, after all, visiting underwater ruins is almost impossible in the real world.\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n 	<li>Key requirements of the concept</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThis concept can be mainly divided into two parts. One is the environment, which includes ruins, uneven seabed, sea creatures, water surface and environment rendering, etc. The other is interactive content, which is mainly player-related functions. In terms of building the environment, I checked some underwater scenes in the Future Boy Conan. I recreated the scene on a small scale using the assets I could easily; For player characters, I used the XR Interaction Toolkit as the support of the VR platform and implemented different functions through a series of codes.\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n 	<li>Why the application should be considered to be a virtual reality experience?</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe game has to be played using a VR headset, combined with the content of the application, it\'s a clearly virtual reality experience.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1>Required functionality:</h1>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Various form of control\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Continuous Movement</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nTo enable Continuous movement, I created a script called the Continuous Motion System, which reads the orientation of the player\'s headset and moves the player in that direction. When the player is on the surface (ground layer), the player can only move on the X-axis, and when the player is underwater, the player can move on both the X-axis and the Y-axis.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','SIT283 Assessment 2  Marine Park Development Report','','draft','open','open','','','','','2023-04-24 10:56:18','2023-04-24 00:56:18','',0,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=43',0,'post','',0),(44,1,'2023-04-24 10:56:18','2023-04-24 00:56:18','<h1>Introduction</h1>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Concept: Marine Park</li>\r\n 	<li>Context of the Concept:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe idea of constructing this underwater world came from an animation I watched when I was a child, called Future Boy Conan, which tells the story of the protagonist and his grandfather living on an island after more than half of the earth\'s land was destroyed in a war. In the early stages of the story, the underwater ruins are impressive, this scenario may be as anti-war propaganda, perhaps can make people recall childhood memories, or can be as simple as an experience of visiting ruins in the underwater world, after all, visiting underwater ruins is almost impossible in the real world.\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n 	<li>Key requirements of the concept</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThis concept can be mainly divided into two parts. One is the environment, which includes ruins, uneven seabed, sea creatures, water surface and environment rendering, etc. The other is interactive content, which is mainly player-related functions. In terms of building the environment, I checked some underwater scenes in the Future Boy Conan. I recreated the scene on a small scale using the assets I could easily; For player characters, I used the XR Interaction Toolkit as the support of the VR platform and implemented different functions through a series of codes.\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n 	<li>Why the application should be considered to be a virtual reality experience?</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe game has to be played using a VR headset, combined with the content of the application, it\'s a clearly virtual reality experience.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1>Required functionality:</h1>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Various form of control\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Continuous Movement</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nTo enable Continuous movement, I created a script called the Continuous Motion System, which reads the orientation of the player\'s headset and moves the player in that direction. When the player is on the surface (ground layer), the player can only move on the X-axis, and when the player is underwater, the player can move on both the X-axis and the Y-axis.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','SIT283 Assessment 2  Marine Park Development Report','','inherit','closed','closed','','43-revision-v1','','','2023-04-24 10:56:18','2023-04-24 00:56:18','',43,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=44',0,'revision','',0),(45,1,'2023-04-24 23:17:08','2023-04-24 13:17:08','','Icon_26_Piano Keyboard','','inherit','open','closed','','icon_26_piano-keyboard','','','2023-04-24 23:17:08','2023-04-24 13:17:08','',0,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Icon_26_Piano-Keyboard.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(46,1,'2023-04-24 23:17:28','2023-04-24 13:17:28','','Icon_26_Piano Keyboard','','inherit','open','closed','','icon_26_piano-keyboard-2','','','2023-05-02 11:51:23','2023-05-02 01:51:23','',0,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Icon_26_Piano-Keyboard-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(48,1,'2023-04-27 16:52:40','2023-04-27 06:52:40','<h3 id=\"header-id-1\">1. 什么是LNMP架构</h3>\r\nLNMP是常见的单机架构，通常用于业务的早期阶段或是个人业务，如博客；LNMP即 Linux系统+Nginx Web server+Mysql数据库+PHP后端程序的统称；\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 id=\"header-id-2\">2. LNMP架构原理</h3>\r\nLNMP工作流是的当用户通过浏览器访问Web服务时，其静态请求交由Nginx Web Server来处理，而动态请求则由Nginx通过FastCGI接口转发给本机的后端程序，即php-fpm进程进行解析；\r\n\r\n如果该请求需要读取MySQL数据库，则php-fpm会继续向后读取MySQL数据库，并一层一层地返回数据，最后由Nginx将数据返回给用户。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 id=\"header-id-3\">3. 部署LNMP环境</h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-4\">1) 创建Nginx运行用户</h4>\r\n其实这部并非必要，yum安装Nginx的话安装过程中会自动创建一个Nginx用户，但是我习惯了用www用户来跑Web Server，所以还是创建一个。\r\n<pre class=\"code\">groupadd www -g 500\r\nuseradd www -s /sbin/nologin -M -u 500 -g 500</pre>\r\n之后可以用id www命令来检查一下用户创建是否成功。\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-5\">2) 安装Nginx，PHP和MySQL</h4>\r\n安装Nginx\r\n<pre class=\"code\">yum insatll nginx -y</pre>\r\n先删除PHP旧环境\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<pre class=\"code\">yum remove php* -y</pre>\r\n配置PHP的yum源和第三方源\r\n<pre class=\"code\">rpm -Uvh https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm\r\nrpm -Uvh https://mirror.webtatic.com/yum/el7/webtatic-release.rpm</pre>\r\n安装php-fpm及其依赖\r\n<pre class=\"code\">yum install -y php71w-cli php71w-common php71w-devel php71w-embedded php71w-gd php71w-mcrypt php71w-mbstring php71w-pdo php71w-xml php71w-fpm php71w-mysqlnd php71w-opcache php71w-pecl-memcached php71w-pecl-redis php71w-pecl-mongodb php71w-json php71w-pecl-apcu php71w-pecl-apcu-devel</pre>\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-6\">3) 配置php-fpm和Nginx用户一致</h4>\r\n这里直接用sed改了\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<pre class=\"code\">sed -i \'/^user/c user = www\' /etc/php-fpm.d/www.conf\r\nsed -i \'/^group/c group = www\' /etc/php-fpm.d/www.conf</pre>\r\n或者也可以直接用Vim编辑/etc/php-fpm.d/www.conf文件，将第8行和第10行的user和group都等于www就行。\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-7\">4) 部署MySQL</h4>\r\nyum install mariadb-server mariadb -y\r\n\r\n很多人疑惑为什么MySQL叫做mariadb，其实就是MySQL在闭源后原开发者基于源MySQL代码之上进行二次开发的产物，两者虽然略有差异，但很多底层的内容都是兼容的。由于开源的CentOS7已经不再支持MySQL，所以只能用mariadb。\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-8\">5) 启动服务并设置开机自启</h4>\r\n<pre class=\"code\">systemctl start nginx\r\nsystemctl enable nginx\r\n\r\nsystemctl start php-fpm\r\nsystemctl enable php-fpm\r\n\r\nsystemctl start mariadb\r\nsystemctl enable mariadb</pre>\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-9\">6) MySQL初始化设置</h4>\r\nroot是MySQL的默认管理员用户，我们首先要为其设置密码。\r\n\r\nmysqladmin password \'password\' #password用自己的密码进行替换\r\n\r\n测试登录\r\n\r\nmysql -uroot -ppassword #-u 后面跟root用户名 -p后面跟用户名对应的密码\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 id=\"header-id-11\">4. 修改Nginx配置文件使其支持FastCGI</h3>\r\n需要使用fastcgi_pass请求转发和fastcgi_param变量\r\n\r\n官方文档：https://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_fastcgi_module.html#fastcgi_pass      https://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_fastcgi_module.html#fastcgi_index\r\n\r\n配置示例：\r\n\r\n首先进入/etc/nginx/nginx.conf文件，确保include /etc/nginx/conf.d/*.conf;该行未被注释掉。\r\n\r\n然后进入include /etc/nginx/conf.d/目录内，新建一个.conf文件。\r\n<pre class=\"code\">server{\r\n     listen 80;\r\n     server_name _;\r\n     # 静态请求，资源存放路径\r\n     root /code;\r\n     index index.php index.html;\r\n     # 动态请求处理\r\n     location ~ \\.php$ {\r\n          root /code;\r\n          fastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;\r\n          fastcgi_index index.php;\r\n          fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;\r\n          include fastcgi_params;\r\n     }\r\n}</pre>\r\n其中$document_root 表示当前locatin设置的root或是alias的目录，SCRIPT_FILENAME 用于在php中确定脚本名字，fastcgi_script_name 为请求的URL。\r\n\r\nlocation ~ \\.php$ 是一个匹配规则，意思是所有以.php结尾的请求都会交由这个location下的配置进行处理也就是交由位于本机9000端口的php后端程序来处理。\r\n\r\n创建phpinfo测试文件\r\n\r\n首先创建之前在配置文件中写入的文件存放目录\r\n<pre class=\"code\">mkdir /code</pre>\r\n然后创建phpinfo文件\r\n<pre class=\"code\">touch /code/phpinfo.php\r\ncat &gt;&gt; /code/phpinfo.php &lt;&lt; EOF\r\n&lt;?php\r\nphpinfo();\r\n?&gt;\r\nEOF</pre>\r\n检查nginx语法并重载配置文件\r\n\r\n接下来可以使用ip/phpinfo.php，如192.168.0.7/phpinfo.php来查看是否成功。出现类似下面的页面就说明我们发送的动态请求成功地被nginx通过fastcgi转发给php后端进行处理了。\r\n<h3 id=\"header-id-12\">5. 测试与MySQL的链接</h3>\r\n在/code目录下新建一个mysql-test.php文件，并写入如下内容\r\n<pre class=\"code\">&lt;?php\r\n     $server=\"127.0.0.1\";\r\n     $mysql_user=\"root\";\r\n     $mysql_pwd=\"123456\";\r\n     // 创建数据库连接\r\n     $conn=mysqli_connect($server,$mysql_user,$mysql_pwd);\r\n     // 检测连通性\r\n     if($conn){\r\n          echo \"Connect to mysql database successful \\n\";\r\n     }else {\r\n          die( \"Connection failed: \" . mysqli_connect_error());\r\n     }\r\n?&gt;</pre>\r\n然后访问ip/mysql-test.php文件，如果显示”Connect to mysql database successful”则说明与PHP与MySQL的链接正常。\r\n\r\n至此，LNMP架构就成功部署了。现在访问你的IP应该可以得到一个CentOS的介绍页面。\r\n<h3 id=\"header-id-13\">6. 部署Wordpress</h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-14\">1)  创建虚拟主机的配置文件</h4>\r\n<pre class=\"code\">server{\r\n     listen 80;\r\n     server_name blog.free.cc;\r\n     # 静态请求，资源存放路径\r\n     root /code/wordpress;\r\n     index index.php index.html;\r\n     # 动态请求处理\r\n     location ~ \\.php$ {\r\n          root /code/wordpress;\r\n          fastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;\r\n          fastcgi_index index.php;\r\n          fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;\r\n          include fastcgi_params;\r\n     }\r\n}</pre>\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-15\">2) 下载wordpress源码</h4>\r\n<pre class=\"code\">cd /code/ ; wget https://cn.wordpress.org/latest-zh_CN.zip</pre>\r\n解压缩\r\n<pre class=\"code\">unzip latest-zh_CN.zip</pre>\r\n授权\r\n<pre class=\"code\">chown -R www.www /code/</pre>\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-16\">3) 创建MySQL数据库</h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<pre class=\"code\">mysql -uroot -ppassword</pre>\r\n<pre class=\"code\">create database database_name;</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4 id=\"header-id-17\">4)进行wordpress安装</h4>\r\n访问你的IP地址，可以看见一个安装导航界面\r\n\r\n<strong>数据库名</strong>填你刚刚自己创建的数据库名称；\r\n\r\n<strong>数据库主机</strong>填localhost:<strong>3306</strong>\r\n\r\n表前缀不重要，可改可不改。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n完成安装后就进入到了Wordpress后台，开始创造自己的网站把！\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 id=\"header-id-13\">6. 一键部署LNMP脚本</h3>','单机部署LNMP架构','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-revision-v1','','','2023-04-27 16:52:40','2023-04-27 06:52:40','',7,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=48',0,'revision','',0),(50,1,'2023-04-27 17:06:20','2023-04-27 07:06:20','','Deploy_LNMP.sh','','inherit','open','closed','','deploy_lnmp-sh','','','2023-04-27 17:06:20','2023-04-27 07:06:20','',0,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Deploy_LNMP.sh.sh',0,'attachment','text/x-sh',0),(51,1,'2023-04-27 17:06:46','2023-04-27 07:06:46','<h3 id=\"header-id-1\">1. 什么是LNMP架构</h3>\n<p>LNMP是常见的单机架构，通常用于业务的早期阶段或是个人业务，如博客；LNMP即 Linux系统+Nginx Web server+Mysql数据库+PHP后端程序的统称；</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 id=\"header-id-2\">2. LNMP架构原理</h3>\n<p>LNMP工作流是的当用户通过浏览器访问Web服务时，其静态请求交由Nginx Web Server来处理，而动态请求则由Nginx通过FastCGI接口转发给本机的后端程序，即php-fpm进程进行解析；</p>\n<p>如果该请求需要读取MySQL数据库，则php-fpm会继续向后读取MySQL数据库，并一层一层地返回数据，最后由Nginx将数据返回给用户。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 id=\"header-id-3\">3. 部署LNMP环境</h3>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-4\">1) 创建Nginx运行用户</h4>\n<p>其实这部并非必要，yum安装Nginx的话安装过程中会自动创建一个Nginx用户，但是我习惯了用www用户来跑Web Server，所以还是创建一个。</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">groupadd www -g 500\nuseradd www -s /sbin/nologin -M -u 500 -g 500</pre>\n<p>之后可以用id www命令来检查一下用户创建是否成功。</p>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-5\">2) 安装Nginx，PHP和MySQL</h4>\n<p>安装Nginx</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">yum insatll nginx -y</pre>\n<p>先删除PHP旧环境</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">yum remove php* -y</pre>\n<p>配置PHP的yum源和第三方源</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">rpm -Uvh https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm\nrpm -Uvh https://mirror.webtatic.com/yum/el7/webtatic-release.rpm</pre>\n<p>安装php-fpm及其依赖</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">yum install -y php71w-cli php71w-common php71w-devel php71w-embedded php71w-gd php71w-mcrypt php71w-mbstring php71w-pdo php71w-xml php71w-fpm php71w-mysqlnd php71w-opcache php71w-pecl-memcached php71w-pecl-redis php71w-pecl-mongodb php71w-json php71w-pecl-apcu php71w-pecl-apcu-devel</pre>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-6\">3) 配置php-fpm和Nginx用户一致</h4>\n<p>这里直接用sed改了</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">sed -i \'/^user/c user = www\' /etc/php-fpm.d/www.conf\nsed -i \'/^group/c group = www\' /etc/php-fpm.d/www.conf</pre>\n<p>或者也可以直接用Vim编辑/etc/php-fpm.d/www.conf文件，将第8行和第10行的user和group都等于www就行。</p>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-7\">4) 部署MySQL</h4>\n<p>yum install mariadb-server mariadb -y</p>\n<p>很多人疑惑为什么MySQL叫做mariadb，其实就是MySQL在闭源后原开发者基于源MySQL代码之上进行二次开发的产物，两者虽然略有差异，但很多底层的内容都是兼容的。由于开源的CentOS7已经不再支持MySQL，所以只能用mariadb。</p>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-8\">5) 启动服务并设置开机自启</h4>\n<pre class=\"code\">systemctl start nginx\nsystemctl enable nginx\n\nsystemctl start php-fpm\nsystemctl enable php-fpm\n\nsystemctl start mariadb\nsystemctl enable mariadb</pre>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-9\">6) MySQL初始化设置</h4>\n<p>root是MySQL的默认管理员用户，我们首先要为其设置密码。</p>\n<p>mysqladmin password \'password\' #password用自己的密码进行替换</p>\n<p>测试登录</p>\n<p>mysql -uroot -ppassword #-u 后面跟root用户名 -p后面跟用户名对应的密码</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 id=\"header-id-11\">4. 修改Nginx配置文件使其支持FastCGI</h3>\n<p>需要使用fastcgi_pass请求转发和fastcgi_param变量</p>\n<p>官方文档：https://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_fastcgi_module.html#fastcgi_pass&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; https://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_fastcgi_module.html#fastcgi_index</p>\n<p>配置示例：</p>\n<p>首先进入/etc/nginx/nginx.conf文件，确保include /etc/nginx/conf.d/*.conf;该行未被注释掉。</p>\n<p>然后进入include /etc/nginx/conf.d/目录内，新建一个.conf文件。</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">server{\n     listen 80;\n     server_name _;\n     # 静态请求，资源存放路径\n     root /code;\n     index index.php index.html;\n     # 动态请求处理\n     location ~ \\.php$ {\n          root /code;\n          fastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;\n          fastcgi_index index.php;\n          fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;\n          include fastcgi_params;\n     }\n}</pre>\n<p>其中$document_root 表示当前locatin设置的root或是alias的目录，SCRIPT_FILENAME 用于在php中确定脚本名字，fastcgi_script_name 为请求的URL。</p>\n<p>location ~ \\.php$ 是一个匹配规则，意思是所有以.php结尾的请求都会交由这个location下的配置进行处理也就是交由位于本机9000端口的php后端程序来处理。</p>\n<p>创建phpinfo测试文件</p>\n<p>首先创建之前在配置文件中写入的文件存放目录</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">mkdir /code</pre>\n<p>然后创建phpinfo文件</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">touch /code/phpinfo.php\ncat &gt;&gt; /code/phpinfo.php &lt;&lt; EOF\n&lt;?php\nphpinfo();\n?&gt;\nEOF</pre>\n<p>检查nginx语法并重载配置文件</p>\n<p>接下来可以使用ip/phpinfo.php，如192.168.0.7/phpinfo.php来查看是否成功。出现类似下面的页面就说明我们发送的动态请求成功地被nginx通过fastcgi转发给php后端进行处理了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"header-id-12\">5. 测试与MySQL的链接</h3>\n<p>在/code目录下新建一个mysql-test.php文件，并写入如下内容</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">&lt;?php\n     $server=\"127.0.0.1\";\n     $mysql_user=\"root\";\n     $mysql_pwd=\"123456\";\n     // 创建数据库连接\n     $conn=mysqli_connect($server,$mysql_user,$mysql_pwd);\n     // 检测连通性\n     if($conn){\n          echo \"Connect to mysql database successful \\n\";\n     }else {\n          die( \"Connection failed: \" . mysqli_connect_error());\n     }\n?&gt;</pre>\n<p>然后访问ip/mysql-test.php文件，如果显示”Connect to mysql database successful”则说明与PHP与MySQL的链接正常。</p>\n<p>至此，LNMP架构就成功部署了。现在访问你的IP应该可以得到一个CentOS的介绍页面。</p>\n<h3 id=\"header-id-13\">6. 部署Wordpress</h3>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-14\">1)&nbsp; 创建虚拟主机的配置文件</h4>\n<pre class=\"code\">server{\n     listen 80;\n     server_name blog.free.cc;\n     # 静态请求，资源存放路径\n     root /code/wordpress;\n     index index.php index.html;\n     # 动态请求处理\n     location ~ \\.php$ {\n          root /code/wordpress;\n          fastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;\n          fastcgi_index index.php;\n          fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;\n          include fastcgi_params;\n     }\n}</pre>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-15\">2) 下载wordpress源码</h4>\n<pre class=\"code\">cd /code/ ; wget https://cn.wordpress.org/latest-zh_CN.zip</pre>\n<p>解压缩</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">unzip latest-zh_CN.zip</pre>\n<p>授权</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">chown -R www.www /code/</pre>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-16\">3) 创建MySQL数据库</h4>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<pre class=\"code\">mysql -uroot -ppassword</pre>\n<pre class=\"code\">create database database_name;</pre>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4 id=\"header-id-17\">4)进行wordpress安装</h4>\n<p>访问你的IP地址，可以看见一个安装导航界面</p>\n<p><strong>数据库名</strong>填你刚刚自己创建的数据库名称；</p>\n<p><strong>数据库主机</strong>填localhost:<strong>3306</strong></p>\n<p>表前缀不重要，可改可不改。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>完成安装后就进入到了Wordpress后台，开始创造自己的网站把！</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 id=\"header-id-13\">6. 一键部署LNMP脚本</h3>\n\n<!-- wp:file {\"id\":50,\"href\":\"https://www.freelytomorrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Deploy_LNMP.sh.sh\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-de539cae-255e-4a38-b0e3-3afdbff94d9e\" href=\"https://www.freelytomorrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Deploy_LNMP.sh.sh\">Deploy_LNMP.sh</a><a href=\"https://www.freelytomorrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Deploy_LNMP.sh.sh\" class=\"wp-block-file__button wp-element-button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-de539cae-255e-4a38-b0e3-3afdbff94d9e\">下载</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->','单机部署LNMP架构','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-revision-v1','','','2023-04-27 17:06:46','2023-04-27 07:06:46','',7,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=51',0,'revision','',0),(53,1,'2023-02-22 15:52:32','2023-02-22 04:52:32','<h3>代码：</h3>\r\n<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash \r\n\r\n# *************************************************************************** #\r\n# * \r\n# * @file:restart_services.sh \r\n# * @author:CHUNYI WANG \r\n# * @date:2023-04-29 18:27 \r\n# * @version 1.0 \r\n# * @description: A shell script used to restart some services.\r\n# * \r\n# ************************************************************************** # +\r\n\r\nservices_list=(mariadb php-fpm nginx) #A list used to store services that need to get started or restarted\r\ndeclare -A result #A map used to store the result of start or restart operations\r\n\r\nemail=\"****.com\"\r\nsmtp_server=\"smtp.qq.com:465\"\r\npasswd=\"********\"\r\ncert=\"qq.crt\"\r\n\r\n## This function is used to determine whether the service has successfully started or restarted, and carry out further commands (send notification email and write the log)\r\nfunction isSuccess(){\r\n    local service=$1\r\n    if [ $2 != 0 ]; then\r\n        result[${service}]=0\r\n        echo -e \"Service ${service} restart failed.\" | mail -s \"System warning\" \"${email}\"\r\n        generate_log ${service} \"FAILED\"\r\n    else\r\n        result[${service}]=1\r\n        generate_log ${service} \"SUCCESS\"\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\n## This function is used to start or restart services\r\nfunction restart_service(){\r\n    local service=$1\r\n    status=$(systemctl status \"${service}\" | grep Active | awk \'{print $2}\')\r\n    if [ \"${status}\" != \'active\' ]; then\r\n        systemctl start \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n    else\r\n        systemctl restart \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\n## Check if all services have successfully restarted, if so, send a notification email to administartor, otherwise the warning will be sent via the isSuccess() function.\r\nfunction isAllSuccess(){\r\n    local allSuccess=true\r\n    for key in ${!result[@]}\r\n    do\r\n        if [ \"${key}\" != \"1\" ]; then\r\n            allSuccess=false\r\n            break\r\n        fi\r\n    done\r\n\r\n    if [ ${allSuccess} ]; then\r\n        echo -e \"All services has successfully restarted\" | mail -s \"System notification\" \"${email}\"\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\n## Used to write the log\r\nfunction generate_log(){\r\n    local logPath=\"/home/centos/service_restart.log\"\r\n    echo \"$(date \"+%F - %T\") $1 restart $2\" &gt;&gt; ${logPath}\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction main(){\r\n    for (( i=0; i&lt;${#services_list[@]}; i++ ))\r\n    do\r\n        restart_service ${services_list[$i]}\r\n    done\r\n}\r\n\r\nmain\r\n\r\nisAllSuccess\r\n\r\nexit 0</pre>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>Crontab定时任务配置示例</h3>\r\n<pre class=\"code\"> 0 0 * * * /home/centos/scripts/restart_services.sh</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>代码下载</h3>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelytomorrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/restart_services.sh\">restart_services</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','一个用于自动重启服务的shell脚本','','publish','open','open','','%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aa%e7%94%a8%e4%ba%8e%e8%87%aa%e5%8a%a8%e9%87%8d%e5%90%af%e6%9c%8d%e5%8a%a1%e7%9a%84shell%e8%84%9a%e6%9c%ac','','','2023-05-01 14:21:47','2023-05-01 04:21:47','',0,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=53',0,'post','',0),(54,1,'2023-04-30 15:46:22','2023-04-30 05:46:22','<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash \r\n\r\n# *************************************************************************** #\r\n# * \r\n# * @file:restart_services.sh \r\n# * @author:CHUNYI WANG \r\n# * @date:2023-04-29 18:27 \r\n# * @version 1.0 \r\n# * @description: A shell script used to restart some services.\r\n# * \r\n# ************************************************************************** # +\r\n\r\nservices_list=(mariadb php-fpm nginx) #A list used to store services that need to get started or restarted\r\ndeclare -A result #A map used to store the result of start or restart operations\r\n\r\nemail=\"****.com\"\r\nsmtp_server=\"smtp.qq.com:465\"\r\npasswd=\"ysdswkyywbosbbdb\"\r\ncert=\"qq.crt\"\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','一个用于自动重启服务的shell脚本','','inherit','closed','closed','','53-revision-v1','','','2023-04-30 15:46:22','2023-04-30 05:46:22','',53,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=54',0,'revision','',0),(55,1,'2023-04-30 15:47:17','2023-04-30 05:47:17','<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash \n\n# *************************************************************************** #\n# * \n# * @file:restart_services.sh \n# * @author:CHUNYI WANG \n# * @date:2023-04-29 18:27 \n# * @version 1.0 \n# * @description: A shell script used to restart some services.\n# * \n# ************************************************************************** # +\n\nservices_list=(mariadb php-fpm nginx) #A list used to store services that need to get started or restarted\ndeclare -A result #A map used to store the result of start or restart operations\n\nemail=\"****.com\"\nsmtp_server=\"smtp.qq.com:465\"\npasswd=\"ysdswkyywbosbbdb\"\ncert=\"qq.crt\"\n\n## This function is used to determine whether the service has successfully started or restarted, and carry out further commands (send notification email and write the log)\nfunction isSuccess(){\n    local service=$1\n    if [ $2 != 0 ]; then\n        result[${service}]=0\n        echo -e \"Service ${service} restart failed.\" | mail -s \"System warning\" \"${email}\"\n        generate_log ${service} \"FAILED\"\n    else\n        result[${service}]=1\n        generate_log ${service} \"SUCCESS\"\n    fi\n}\n\n\n</pre>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"code\">\n\n</pre>','一个用于自动重启服务的shell脚本','','inherit','closed','closed','','53-revision-v1','','','2023-04-30 15:47:17','2023-04-30 05:47:17','',53,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=55',0,'revision','',0),(56,1,'2023-04-30 15:50:09','2023-04-30 05:50:09','<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash \n\n# *************************************************************************** #\n# * \n# * @file:restart_services.sh \n# * @author:CHUNYI WANG \n# * @date:2023-04-29 18:27 \n# * @version 1.0 \n# * @description: A shell script used to restart some services.\n# * \n# ************************************************************************** # +\n\nservices_list=(mariadb php-fpm nginx) #A list used to store services that need to get started or restarted\ndeclare -A result #A map used to store the result of start or restart operations\n\nemail=\"****.com\"\nsmtp_server=\"smtp.qq.com:465\"\npasswd=\"ysdswkyywbosbbdb\"\ncert=\"qq.crt\"\n\n## This function is used to determine whether the service has successfully started or restarted, and carry out further commands (send notification email and write the log)\nfunction isSuccess(){\n    local service=$1\n    if [ $2 != 0 ]; then\n        result[${service}]=0\n        echo -e \"Service ${service} restart failed.\" | mail -s \"System warning\" \"${email}\"\n        generate_log ${service} \"FAILED\"\n    else\n        result[${service}]=1\n        generate_log ${service} \"SUCCESS\"\n    fi\n}\n\n## This function is used to start or restart services\nfunction restart_service(){\n    local service=$1\n    status=$(systemctl status \"${service}\" | grep Active | awk \'{print $2}\')\n    if [ \"${status}\" != \'active\' ]; then\n        systemctl start \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n    else\n        systemctl restart \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n    fi\n}\n\n## Check if all services have successfully restarted, if so, send a notification email to administartor, otherwise the warning will be sent via the isSuccess() function.\nfunction isAllSuccess(){\n    local allSuccess=true\n    for key in ${!result[@]}\n    do\n        if [ \"${key}\" != \"1\" ]; then\n            allSuccess=false\n            break\n        fi\n    done\n\n    if [ ${allSuccess} ]; then\n        echo -e \"All services has successfully restarted\" | mail -s \"System notification\" \"${email}\"\n    fi\n}\n\n## Used to write the log\nfunction generate_log(){\n    local logPath=\"/home/centos/service_restart.log\"\n    echo \"$(date \"+%F - %T\") $1 restart $2\" &gt;&gt; ${logPath}\n}\n\nfunction main(){\n    for (( i=0; i&lt;${#services_list[@]}; i++ ))\n    do\n        restart_service ${services_list[$i]}\n    done\n}\n\nmain\n\nisAllSuccess\n\nexit 0</pre>\n<pre class=\"code\">\n\n</pre>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n</div>','一个用于自动重启服务的shell脚本','','inherit','closed','closed','','53-revision-v1','','','2023-04-30 15:50:09','2023-04-30 05:50:09','',53,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=56',0,'revision','',0),(57,1,'2023-04-30 15:50:32','2023-04-30 05:50:32','<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash \n\n# *************************************************************************** #\n# * \n# * @file:restart_services.sh \n# * @author:CHUNYI WANG \n# * @date:2023-04-29 18:27 \n# * @version 1.0 \n# * @description: A shell script used to restart some services.\n# * \n# ************************************************************************** # +\n\nservices_list=(mariadb php-fpm nginx) #A list used to store services that need to get started or restarted\ndeclare -A result #A map used to store the result of start or restart operations\n\nemail=\"****.com\"\nsmtp_server=\"smtp.qq.com:465\"\npasswd=\"ysdswkyywbosbbdb\"\ncert=\"qq.crt\"\n\n## This function is used to determine whether the service has successfully started or restarted, and carry out further commands (send notification email and write the log)\nfunction isSuccess(){\n    local service=$1\n    if [ $2 != 0 ]; then\n        result[${service}]=0\n        echo -e \"Service ${service} restart failed.\" | mail -s \"System warning\" \"${email}\"\n        generate_log ${service} \"FAILED\"\n    else\n        result[${service}]=1\n        generate_log ${service} \"SUCCESS\"\n    fi\n}\n\n## This function is used to start or restart services\nfunction restart_service(){\n    local service=$1\n    status=$(systemctl status \"${service}\" | grep Active | awk \'{print $2}\')\n    if [ \"${status}\" != \'active\' ]; then\n        systemctl start \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n    else\n        systemctl restart \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n    fi\n}\n\n## Check if all services have successfully restarted, if so, send a notification email to administartor, otherwise the warning will be sent via the isSuccess() function.\nfunction isAllSuccess(){\n    local allSuccess=true\n    for key in ${!result[@]}\n    do\n        if [ \"${key}\" != \"1\" ]; then\n            allSuccess=false\n            break\n        fi\n    done\n\n    if [ ${allSuccess} ]; then\n        echo -e \"All services has successfully restarted\" | mail -s \"System notification\" \"${email}\"\n    fi\n}\n\n## Used to write the log\nfunction generate_log(){\n    local logPath=\"/home/centos/service_restart.log\"\n    echo \"$(date \"+%F - %T\") $1 restart $2\" &gt;&gt; ${logPath}\n}\n\nfunction main(){\n    for (( i=0; i&lt;${#services_list[@]}; i++ ))\n    do\n        restart_service ${services_list[$i]}\n    done\n}\n\nmain\n\nisAllSuccess\n\nexit 0</pre>','一个用于自动重启服务的shell脚本','','inherit','closed','closed','','53-revision-v1','','','2023-04-30 15:50:32','2023-04-30 05:50:32','',53,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=57',0,'revision','',0),(58,1,'2023-04-30 15:52:10','2023-04-30 05:52:10','<pre>自己定义email变量，如果不使用qq邮箱，请自行查看对应邮箱的smtp配置</pre>\r\n<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash \r\n\r\n# *************************************************************************** #\r\n# * \r\n# * @file:restart_services.sh \r\n# * @author:CHUNYI WANG \r\n# * @date:2023-04-29 18:27 \r\n# * @version 1.0 \r\n# * @description: A shell script used to restart some services.\r\n# * \r\n# ************************************************************************** # +\r\n\r\nservices_list=(mariadb php-fpm nginx) #A list used to store services that need to get started or restarted\r\ndeclare -A result #A map used to store the result of start or restart operations\r\n\r\nemail=\"****.com\"\r\nsmtp_server=\"smtp.qq.com:465\"\r\npasswd=\"ysdswkyywbosbbdb\"\r\ncert=\"qq.crt\"\r\n\r\n## This function is used to determine whether the service has successfully started or restarted, and carry out further commands (send notification email and write the log)\r\nfunction isSuccess(){\r\n    local service=$1\r\n    if [ $2 != 0 ]; then\r\n        result[${service}]=0\r\n        echo -e \"Service ${service} restart failed.\" | mail -s \"System warning\" \"${email}\"\r\n        generate_log ${service} \"FAILED\"\r\n    else\r\n        result[${service}]=1\r\n        generate_log ${service} \"SUCCESS\"\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\n## This function is used to start or restart services\r\nfunction restart_service(){\r\n    local service=$1\r\n    status=$(systemctl status \"${service}\" | grep Active | awk \'{print $2}\')\r\n    if [ \"${status}\" != \'active\' ]; then\r\n        systemctl start \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n    else\r\n        systemctl restart \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\n## Check if all services have successfully restarted, if so, send a notification email to administartor, otherwise the warning will be sent via the isSuccess() function.\r\nfunction isAllSuccess(){\r\n    local allSuccess=true\r\n    for key in ${!result[@]}\r\n    do\r\n        if [ \"${key}\" != \"1\" ]; then\r\n            allSuccess=false\r\n            break\r\n        fi\r\n    done\r\n\r\n    if [ ${allSuccess} ]; then\r\n        echo -e \"All services has successfully restarted\" | mail -s \"System notification\" \"${email}\"\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\n## Used to write the log\r\nfunction generate_log(){\r\n    local logPath=\"/home/centos/service_restart.log\"\r\n    echo \"$(date \"+%F - %T\") $1 restart $2\" &gt;&gt; ${logPath}\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction main(){\r\n    for (( i=0; i&lt;${#services_list[@]}; i++ ))\r\n    do\r\n        restart_service ${services_list[$i]}\r\n    done\r\n}\r\n\r\nmain\r\n\r\nisAllSuccess\r\n\r\nexit 0</pre>','一个用于自动重启服务的shell脚本','','inherit','closed','closed','','53-revision-v1','','','2023-04-30 15:52:10','2023-04-30 05:52:10','',53,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=58',0,'revision','',0),(59,1,'2023-04-30 16:04:53','2023-04-30 06:04:53','<h3>代码：\n自己定义email变量，如果不使用qq邮箱，请自行查看对应邮箱的smtp配置</h3>\n<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash \n\n# *************************************************************************** #\n# * \n# * @file:restart_services.sh \n# * @author:CHUNYI WANG \n# * @date:2023-04-29 18:27 \n# * @version 1.0 \n# * @description: A shell script used to restart some services.\n# * \n# ************************************************************************** # +\n\nservices_list=(mariadb php-fpm nginx) #A list used to store services that need to get started or restarted\ndeclare -A result #A map used to store the result of start or restart operations\n\nemail=\"****.com\"\nsmtp_server=\"smtp.qq.com:465\"\npasswd=\"ysdswkyywbosbbdb\"\ncert=\"qq.crt\"\n\n## This function is used to determine whether the service has successfully started or restarted, and carry out further commands (send notification email and write the log)\nfunction isSuccess(){\n    local service=$1\n    if [ $2 != 0 ]; then\n        result[${service}]=0\n        echo -e \"Service ${service} restart failed.\" | mail -s \"System warning\" \"${email}\"\n        generate_log ${service} \"FAILED\"\n    else\n        result[${service}]=1\n        generate_log ${service} \"SUCCESS\"\n    fi\n}\n\n## This function is used to start or restart services\nfunction restart_service(){\n    local service=$1\n    status=$(systemctl status \"${service}\" | grep Active | awk \'{print $2}\')\n    if [ \"${status}\" != \'active\' ]; then\n        systemctl start \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n    else\n        systemctl restart \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\n    fi\n}\n\n## Check if all services have successfully restarted, if so, send a notification email to administartor, otherwise the warning will be sent via the isSuccess() function.\nfunction isAllSuccess(){\n    local allSuccess=true\n    for key in ${!result[@]}\n    do\n        if [ \"${key}\" != \"1\" ]; then\n            allSuccess=false\n            break\n        fi\n    done\n\n    if [ ${allSuccess} ]; then\n        echo -e \"All services has successfully restarted\" | mail -s \"System notification\" \"${email}\"\n    fi\n}\n\n## Used to write the log\nfunction generate_log(){\n    local logPath=\"/home/centos/service_restart.log\"\n    echo \"$(date \"+%F - %T\") $1 restart $2\" &gt;&gt; ${logPath}\n}\n\nfunction main(){\n    for (( i=0; i&lt;${#services_list[@]}; i++ ))\n    do\n        restart_service ${services_list[$i]}\n    done\n}\n\nmain\n\nisAllSuccess\n\nexit 0</pre>\n可以在crontab定时任务重配置何时自动执行该脚本\n\n&nbsp;','一个用于自动重启服务的shell脚本','','inherit','closed','closed','','53-autosave-v1','','','2023-04-30 16:04:53','2023-04-30 06:04:53','',53,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=59',0,'revision','',0),(60,1,'2023-04-30 15:54:14','2023-04-30 05:54:14','<pre>自己定义email变量，如果不使用qq邮箱，请自行查看对应邮箱的smtp配置</pre>\r\n<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash \r\n\r\n# *************************************************************************** #\r\n# * \r\n# * @file:restart_services.sh \r\n# * @author:CHUNYI WANG \r\n# * @date:2023-04-29 18:27 \r\n# * @version 1.0 \r\n# * @description: A shell script used to restart some services.\r\n# * \r\n# ************************************************************************** # +\r\n\r\nservices_list=(mariadb php-fpm nginx) #A list used to store services that need to get started or restarted\r\ndeclare -A result #A map used to store the result of start or restart operations\r\n\r\nemail=\"****.com\"\r\nsmtp_server=\"smtp.qq.com:465\"\r\npasswd=\"ysdswkyywbosbbdb\"\r\ncert=\"qq.crt\"\r\n\r\n## This function is used to determine whether the service has successfully started or restarted, and carry out further commands (send notification email and write the log)\r\nfunction isSuccess(){\r\n    local service=$1\r\n    if [ $2 != 0 ]; then\r\n        result[${service}]=0\r\n        echo -e \"Service ${service} restart failed.\" | mail -s \"System warning\" \"${email}\"\r\n        generate_log ${service} \"FAILED\"\r\n    else\r\n        result[${service}]=1\r\n        generate_log ${service} \"SUCCESS\"\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\n## This function is used to start or restart services\r\nfunction restart_service(){\r\n    local service=$1\r\n    status=$(systemctl status \"${service}\" | grep Active | awk \'{print $2}\')\r\n    if [ \"${status}\" != \'active\' ]; then\r\n        systemctl start \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n    else\r\n        systemctl restart \"${service}\" &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n        isSuccess \"${service}\" $? &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\n## Check if all services have successfully restarted, if so, send a notification email to administartor, otherwise the warning will be sent via the isSuccess() function.\r\nfunction isAllSuccess(){\r\n    local allSuccess=true\r\n    for key in ${!result[@]}\r\n    do\r\n        if [ \"${key}\" != \"1\" ]; then\r\n            allSuccess=false\r\n            break\r\n        fi\r\n    done\r\n\r\n    if [ ${allSuccess} ]; then\r\n        echo -e \"All services has successfully restarted\" | mail -s \"System notification\" \"${email}\"\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\n## Used to write the log\r\nfunction generate_log(){\r\n    local logPath=\"/home/centos/service_restart.log\"\r\n    echo \"$(date \"+%F - %T\") $1 restart $2\" &gt;&gt; ${logPath}\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction main(){\r\n    for (( i=0; i&lt;${#services_list[@]}; i++ ))\r\n    do\r\n        restart_service ${services_list[$i]}\r\n    done\r\n}\r\n\r\nmain\r\n\r\nisAllSuccess\r\n\r\nexit 0</pre>\r\n可以在crontab定时任务重配置何时自动执行该脚本','一个用于自动重启服务的shell脚本','','inherit','closed','closed','','53-revision-v1','','','2023-04-30 15:54:14','2023-04-30 05:54:14','',53,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=60',0,'revision','',0),(61,1,'2023-03-01 15:56:34','2023-03-01 04:56:34','<h3>用途</h3>\r\n该脚本用于定期检查指定服务的状态(是否启动)，并根据结果执行对应操作\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>代码</h3>\r\n<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash\r\n\r\n# *************************************************************************** #\r\n# *\r\n# * @file:status_monitor.sh\r\n# * @author:CHUNYI WANG\r\n# * @date:2023-04-30 14:57\r\n# * @version 1.0  \r\n# * @description: A Shell script used to monitor the status of web services.\r\n# *\r\n# ************************************************************************** #\r\n\r\nservices=(mariadb php-fpm nginx)\r\n\r\nemail=\"****@qq.com\"\r\nsmtp_server=\"smtp.qq.com:465\"\r\npasswd=\"*********\"\r\ncert=\"qq.crt\"\r\n\r\nfunction check_status(){\r\n    local status=$(systemctl status $1 | grep Active | awk \'{print $2}\')\r\n    if [ $status == \'active\' ]; then\r\n        return 0\r\n    else\r\n        return 1\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction isSuccess(){\r\n    if [ $1 != 0 ]; then\r\n        echo -e \"Service: $2 unavailable\" | mail -s \"System warning\" \"${email}\"\r\n    fi\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction main(){\r\n    for key in ${services[@]}\r\n    do\r\n        if  ! check_status \"${key}\"; then\r\n            systemctl start ${key}\r\n            isSuccess $? ${key}\r\n        fi\r\n    done\r\n}\r\n\r\nmain\r\nexit 0</pre>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h3>Crontab配置</h3>\r\n<pre class=\"code\"> */15 * * * * /home/centos/scripts/status_monitor.sh</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>文件下载</h3>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.freelytomorrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/status_monitor.sh\">status_monitor</a>','一个用于定期检查服务状态的Shell脚本','','publish','open','open','','%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aa%e7%94%a8%e4%ba%8e%e5%ae%9a%e6%9c%9f%e6%a3%80%e6%9f%a5%e6%9c%8d%e5%8a%a1%e7%8a%b6%e6%80%81%e7%9a%84shell%e8%84%9a%e6%9c%ac','','','2023-05-01 14:21:33','2023-05-01 04:21:33','',0,'https://www.freelytomorrow.com/?p=61',0,'post','',0),(62,1,'2023-04-30 16:02:03','2023-04-30 06:02:03','<h3>用途</h3>\r\n该脚本用于定期检查指定服务的状态(是否启动)，并根据结果执行对应操作\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>代码</h3>\r\n<pre class=\"code\">#!/bin/bash\r\n\r\n# *************************************************************************** #\r\n# *\r\n# * @file:stat